---
const formAnchor = '#pre-register';
---

<section id="closing-cta" class="relative py-20 md:py-28 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-emerald-900"></div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.07] pointer-events-none">
    <img
      src="/images/gifs/static/LAB1ACH-Hero.jpg"
      class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-48 rounded-2xl rotate-[-8deg]"
      alt=""
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <img
      src="/images/gifs/static/O2LAV-Hero.jpg"
      class="absolute top-20 right-16 w-40 rounded-2xl rotate-[5deg]"
      alt=""
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <img
      src="/images/gifs/static/K2BOD-Hero.jpg"
      class="absolute bottom-16 left-1/4 w-44 rounded-2xl rotate-[3deg]"
      alt=""
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <img
      src="/images/gifs/static/LAB1SPA-Hero.jpg"
      class="absolute bottom-10 right-1/4 w-36 rounded-2xl rotate-[-4deg]"
      alt=""
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <div
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-500/20 border border-emerald-500/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-6"
    >
      <span class="relative flex h-2.5 w-2.5">
        <span
          class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-emerald-400 opacity-75"
        ></span>
        <span
          class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2.5 w-2.5 bg-emerald-500"
        ></span>
      </span>
      <span class="text-emerald-300 text-sm font-medium">まもなくサービス開始</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
      日本での展開をお楽しみに
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      世界中で愛されているSTEAM教育体験を、日本のご家庭にお届けする準備を進めています。
      事前にお申し込みいただくと、最新情報をいち早くお届けします。
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
      <a
        href={formAnchor}
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 text-white font-bold rounded-full transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/30"
      >
        事前お申し込み →
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">
      ご登録いただいた情報は、KiwiCo Japanからのご案内にのみ使用いたします。
    </p>

    <div
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 mt-8 text-gray-400 text-sm flex-wrap"
    >
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"
          />
        </svg>
        SSL暗号化
      </span>
      <span>5千万個以上キット出荷実績</span>
      <span>100+受賞歴</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
